 ploads/event/lying%20wrong%20horiz_mobilize_20260321135023827181.jpg
DESCRIPTION:Join the Davis Visibility Brigade each Thursday and Sunday to 
 make VISIBLE our opposition to the endless corruption\, incompetence\, and
  immorality of the current regime. We display messages to commuters that a
 im to ACTIVATE\, WAKE-UP\, and EMPATHIZE. 14\,000 people will see our mess
 ages in 90 minutes! We have a lot of fun and receive hundreds of honks\, t
 humbs up\, and power fists. All you have to do it show up and wave! Detail
 s provided upon registration. Look for the email you receive after you reg
 i
LOCATION:Davis\, CA
URL:https://www.mobilize.us/indivisibleyolo/event/791515/
X-SOURCE:Indivisible Yolo (Mobilize)
