 ploads/event/Screenshot%202025-08-22%20094306_20250822170959649858.jpg
DESCRIPTION:NEW TIME! Join the Woodland Visibility Brigade each Thursday a
 t 4:30pm to make the Resistance VISIBLE! We resist the authoritarian and f
 ascist administration with a topical message and publicize upcoming local 
 resistance events. We dance and wave and get lots of friendly honks! You w
 ill receive an immediate confirmation email with parking and location deta
 ils\, and a reminder one hour beforehand. Please make sure you know where 
 you're headed before you set out!
LOCATION:Sports Park Bridge\, Woodland\, CA\, 95776
URL:https://www.mobilize.us/indivisibleyolo/event/782287/
X-SOURCE:Indivisible Yolo (Mobilize)
END:VEVENT
